title: #176 - Annie Lederman& ME
description: Comedian Annie Lederman and I hang out in the Mancave and talk about growing up in Philly, her degenerate youth, drinking hard as fuck in Santa Fe, getting into comedy, getting sober, & the brilliance of Kurt Metzger.
